name: .PAQ8L File Extension
summary: Learn about .PAQ8L files and view a list of programs that open them.

description: File archive created by PAQ8L, an open-source data compression archiver that is the L version of the PAQ8 program; can store multiple files and folders in a single compressed archive.

content: NOTE: PAQ8L files can only be decompressed by the same PAQ version in which they were compressed.
